rformance characteristics, help you gain insight into your models with the Core ML Instrument, and take you through API enhancements to further optimize Core ML integration in your apps.","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"references":{"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC22":{"title":"WWDC22","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Xcode 14, Swift 5.7, iOS 16, macOS 13 (Ventura), tvOS 16, watchOS 9."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"New APIs: "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"WeatherKit"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ScreenCaptureKit"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Swift Regex"},{"type":"text","text":", and more."}],"kind":"article","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC22","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"WWDC22-Icon.png"},{"type":"card","identifier":"WWDC22.jpeg"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc22","role":"collectionGroup"},"https://developer.apple.com/videos/play/wwdc2022/10027":{"identifier":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2022\/10027","checksum":null,"url":"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/videos\/play\/wwdc2022\/10027","type":"download"},"WWDCNotes.png":{"type":"image","alt":null,"identifier":"WWDCNotes.png","variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDCNotes.png"}]},"WWDC22.jpeg":{"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC22.jpeg"}],"alt":null,"identifier":"WWDC22.jpeg","type":"image"},"WWDC22-Icon.png":{"identifier":"WWDC22-Icon.png","alt":null,"variants":[{"traits":["1x","light"],"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC22-Icon.png"}],"type":"image"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC22-10017-Explore-the-machine-learning-development-experience":{"title":"Explore the machine learning development experience","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc22-10017-explore-the-machine-learning-development-experience","role":"sampleCode","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC22-10017-Explore-the-machine-learning-development-experience","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Learn how to bring great machine learning (ML) based experiences to your app. We’ll take you through model discovery, conversion, and training and provide tips and best practices for ML. We’ll share considerations to take into account as you begin your ML journey, demonstrate techniques for evaluating model performance, and explore how you can tune models to achieve real-time performance on device."}],"kind":"article","type":"topic"},"https://wwdcnotes.com/documentation/wwdcnotes/contributing":{"type":"link","url":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing","title":"Learn More…","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"Learn More…","type":"text"}]},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes":{"title":"WWDC Notes","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes","images":[{"type":"icon","identifier":"WWDCNotes.png"}],"role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","abstract":[{"text":"Session notes shared by the community for the community.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://WWDCNotes/documentation/WWDCNotes/WWDC23-10049-Improve-Core-ML-integration-with-async-prediction":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC23-10049-Improve-Core-ML-integration-with-async-prediction","kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc23-10049-improve-core-ml-integration-with-async-prediction","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Learn how to speed up machine learning features in your app with the latest Core ML execution engine improvements and find out how aggressive asset caching can help with inference and faster model loads. We’ll show you some of the latest options for async prediction and discuss considerations for balancing performance with overall memory usage to help you create a highly responsive app. Discover APIs to help you understand and maximize hardware utilization for your models."}],"role":"sampleCode","title":"Improve Core ML integration with async prediction"}}}